Task 2: Social Media Campaign Performance Dashboard

Tool Used:
Power BI

Dataset:
Social Media Advertising Dataset

Description:
Created a Power BI dashboard to analyze social media campaign performance.
The dashboard shows total spend, total clicks, age-wise spend distribution,
and spend trend over time.

Insights:
- Campaign 1178 generated the highest spend and clicks.
- Age group 30â€“39 contributed the highest total spend.
- Overall ad spend shows a decreasing trend over time.
